title: @Canadians: A burlesque version of the 90s kids game show Uh Oh! exists, with host Wink Yahoo
body:
I can't link it here on the boards because it's 19+ content, but oh my god I don't know why this exists, but my sister went to the event and was apparently a participant. 

If you want some kind of idea of what the show was about, here's an episode, complete with cringey 90s Canadian commercials for added nostalgia!

https://youtu.be/3ffqj0e381Q
